Long Description:
The ultimate flawless, buildable coverage with 100% natural ingredients. It can be worn alone or over liquid foundation for an even and long-lasting finish.
PRODUCT DESCRIPTION Silky texture results in an airbrushed finish that won't dry out the skin. Pure earth-derived minerals work to even the skin tone and disguise conditions such as acne, scarring, rosacea or pigmentation. Naturally-derived Titanium and Zinc Oxide provide chemical-free sun protection (SPF 25) to safeguard the skin against harmful UV rays. Key Benefits: ; 100% pure Earth-derived minerals offer effortless blending and an airbrushed finish.Buildable coverage.Free from fillers and harsh chemicals.Won’t clog pores or irritate skin. USAGE & INGREDIENTS  Directions of Use : ;
Turn the internal sifter lid to control the amount of product dispensed.  Replace lid and gently tap to release powder.  Slowly and carefully remove lid while keeping product upright to help prevent mess.  Pick up a small amount of powder with your Vegan Kabuki or Vegan Foundation Brush, and swirl around in the lid to evenly coat for flawless application.  Apply in light, circular motions.  Repeat to build coverage in areas as needed.
Ingredients : ;
Mica (CI 77019); Zinc Oxide (CI 77947); Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891); Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI77499); Ultramarines (CI 77007).
